citep{mayzlin2014promotional,luca2016fake}
\end_layout

\end_inset

. Various strategies are in place to mitigate this concern including publishing reviews only by consumers whose purchases can be verified, highlighting reviews that can be linked to verified purchases using special badges, and relying on fraud-detection algorithms to discard fake reviews.
\end_layout

